column2: SELECT     m.id, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1,     n.objid, n.distance,     o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2, o.flags_g As flags_g, o.flags_r As flags_r, o.flags_i As flags_i into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.MyTable AS m     CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid=o.objid
